      "text": "いや～、本当に僅差での勝利でしたね\n白熱したバトルをありがとうございました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ that was a really close victory!\nThanks for that heated battle!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
