    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、お疲れ様。……惜しかったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ everyone… That was a close one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.5139451981
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですね。出来れば勝ちたかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I wish we could’ve won.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5139451981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "五人の時なら確実に勝てていましたね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we still had five members‚ we definitely would’ve won…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3139451981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.1095006467
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "でもさ、ライブは楽しかったよね\nお客さんもすっごい盛り上がってくれたし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But hey‚ the live was fun‚ right?\nThe audience was super hyped!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.6095010282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.6095006467
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわ。負けたからと言ってくよくよする暇など\n私達にはありませんわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right! We don’t have time to sulk\njust because we lost!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.2559631826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "そう……だよね。ありがとう、芽衣ちゃん、すずちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… you’re right. Thanks‚ Mei-chan‚ Suzu-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.2559631826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.3559616567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "さっそく事務所に戻って\n映像を観ながら反省会をしましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s head back to the office right away\nand have a review session while watching the video!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6910862447
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "会場の外にはマスコミが張ってるから\nいつもとは違う出口を使おう。ついて来てくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The press is waiting outside‚\nso let’s use a different exit than usual. Follow me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
