      "text": "あ、ここの振り付け……。私、無意識に\n五人の時と同じ大きさの動きになってたかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ the choreography here… I think I unconsciously\nended up making movements as big as when we had five members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0788904987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "私もです。つい今までの癖で\n五人いる状態でのステージングにしがちですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too. I tend to do our old staging\nas if we still had five people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.3170757455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "だから、フォーメーションだけ変えても\n動きがこぢんまりして見えるのかもしれませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s probably why even if we just change the formation‚\nour movements look cramped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1666702271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.9219056291
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
